 28, 2020). Tucson daily citizen"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:53.248Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2020271971/", "image_url": [], "index": 6, "language": ["english"], "location": ["arizona", "pima", "pima county", "tucson", "united states"], "number": ["1160179351", "2020271971", "online resource", "2020271970", "2692-6873", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["the tucson citizen ([tucson, arizona]) 1901-1928 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 68.06297, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["arizona", "pima county (ariz.)", "tucson (ariz.)", "pima", "pima county", "newspapers", "tucson", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:01:34.100Z", "title": "The Tucson citizen", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2020271971/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2021220058/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1880", "dates": ["[1880 TO 1880]"], "description": ["Weekly Print began with v. 10, no. 27 (Apr. 17, 1880); ceased with v. 11, no. 13 (Dec. 18, 1880). \"Republican.\" Cf. Lutrell, E. Newspapers and periodials of Ariz., 1950. Vol. X, No. 39 (June 19, 1880); title from caption (Chronicling America's website, viewed Jan. 11, 2021). Vol. XI, No. 13 (December 18, 1880) (Chronicling America's website, viewed Jan. 11, 2021). Arizona weekly citizen 2766-8282 (DLC) 2021220059 (OCoLC)904424375"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:34.166Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2021220058/", "image_url": [], "index": 7, "language": ["english"], "location": ["arizona", "pima", "pima county", "tucson", "united states"], "number": ["o